      "uuid": "843d2210-4833-412e-91cc-f26a43247693",
      "text": " How about \"binge-watching\"? It has a nice comedic effect since it's TV-related but also implies intensity, like: \"They binge-watched each other all night long.\" It's silly while staying tasteful. You could also play with related terms like \"streaming\" or \"channel-surfing\" for similar humorous effect.",
